    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your curse creates a temporary bond between you and your target. As a bonus action, you can magically teleport up to 30 feet to an unoccupied space you can see within 5 feet of the target cursed by your @Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-spells.xr8TQuchvLqaKeOt]{Hex} spell or by a warlock feature of yours, such as @Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-class-features.R7KO3rSiHZMJIyfX]{Hexblade's Curse} and @Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-class-features.tejEUCzkm3R8aWtL]{Sign of Ill Omen}. To teleport in this way, you must be able to see the cursed target.</p>",
